metadata.name: Chemistry Potion
metadata.description: Just like the universe as we know it, the metaverse is full of mystery and secrets. A particular artifact was discovered recently during archaeological research. Magical or simply synthesized by a superior entity, its essence and composition still remain a mystery. But the first tests of this strange artifact seem to show surprising but completely random effects. One thing is indisputable, it has changed the lives of those who have tasted it. 3000 bottles circulate freely in the black market. Do you dare to try the experiment and find out what it could bring you ?
